DOC.brief_summary: This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this trial is to evaluate the safety profile of insulin aspart in subjects with type 1 diabetes having participated in trial ANA/DCD/035.
DOC.brief_title: Safety and Efficacy of Insulin Aspart in Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes
DOC.mesh_term: Insulin degludec, insulin aspart drug combination
DOC.criteria: The subject must have completed the six month controlled treatment period in trial ANA/DCD/035
